        "email": "adilger@thelustrecollective.com",
        "username": "adilger"
      },
      "date": "2020-05-01 09:04:11.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nJames reported seeing new failures on master after the recent batch of landings that included this patch.  He wasn't sure of the exact cause, but it makes sense to hold off patch landings from that group until it is isolated.\n\nJames, could you please point Alex at the recent failures you were looking into.",
